Functions (Parameters & Return Types)
What is a Function?  :->>>   A function is a block of reusable code.

Types of Functions
Simple Function
void greet() {
  print("Hello");
}
No input, no return
Function with Parameters
void greetUser(String name) {
  print("Hello $name");
}

Input: name

✔️ Function with Return Value
int add(int a, int b) {
  return a + b;
}

Output: int

✔️ Arrow Function (Short)
int square(int n) => n * n;
✔️ Optional Parameters
void show(String name, {int age = 18}) {
  print("$name is $age");
}
✔️ Required Named Parameters
void login({required String email, required String password}) {
  print(email);
}

